{"tid":514032,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]沙田人快入","createTime":"2017-12-30T07:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T15:15:23.000Z","uid":154389,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a008d3864eaaaccf11344f04956ecf5f13b4a91","tid":514032,"uid":154389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:08:05.000Z","msg":"小弟係12月28日夜晚8-9點<br />\n係沙田博康街市<br />\n跌左個銀包<br />\n外形係個熊貓頭<br />\n入面有現金400左右<br />\n入面有張好緊要既相<br />\n同埋小弟以前母校既學生證<br />\n兩樣野都對小弟好重要<br />\n有好心人執到既 留個言 <br />\n入面現金都係其次可以當係薄酬<br />\n<br />\n麻煩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e832b74617f07403d44c0814056708606b4c33","tid":514032,"uid":125623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"成兩日先發現 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫你推下 <br />\n<br />\n利申:沙田友<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8928015f2e6beb84bb3efb8da3aa34302d0290","tid":514032,"uid":154389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成兩日先發現 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫你推下 <br />\n<br />\n利申:沙田友&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n個日入到好遠做野 翻黎成個人散哂 <br />\n一時冇留意就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第2日成日係屋企休息冇出過去 唉 知錯架啦真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab4d327750b0efedfe3d772e428c57431d8c550","tid":514032,"uid":29724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:38:47.000Z","msg":"街市跌睇怕搵返既機會都幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50740805110403210a1c1a38900b4ba9e9c029dd","tid":514032,"uid":154389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>街市跌睇怕搵返既機會都幾&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n仲要係巷仔黎 <br />\n我都知冇咩機會<br />\n岩岩落去走左幾轉 睇花叢都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44ccb15f98fbbaffe9b920a28ab286ff569b988","tid":514032,"uid":75,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:40:32.000Z","msg":"唔好講話2日，而家嗰度咁多蝗，蝻，跌咗應該都係咁「大」<br />\n祝巴打好運，幫推"},{"pid":"bbda94224b46a67480ba3dd71c95bf1c16f39acb","tid":514032,"uid":154389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好講話2日，而家嗰度咁多蝗，蝻，跌咗應該都係咁「大」<br />\n祝巴打好運，幫推</blockquote><br />\n蝻就冇乜既 不過我唸都冇咩機會<br />\n拎個小希望姐 多謝巴打幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fbfc329b376d369928416a07252de382d70a24","tid":514032,"uid":154389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:25:58.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3c1745c45cebeb1895d70cc15160c83cc1f8bd","tid":514032,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n但係創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ??"},{"pid":"896dde66b9fc261034ce25781865ec22ae6ac6a9","tid":514032,"uid":154389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推<br />\n但係創意台&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt; ??</blockquote><br />\n唔知應該放咩台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw多謝幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}